PrecisAppointment of an ADMINISTRATOR of the Government of MANITOBA, namely the Hon. ALFRED M. MONNIN, who shall execute the office and functions of the Lieutenant Governor from July 3 to September 4, 1995, during the absence, illness or other inability of the latter.
